Axiom Pplus_1: forall A B, A + B = O <-> A = (-1) * B.
  
Axiom Pmults_1: forall n m A, Pmults (n) (Pmults m A) = Pmults (n * m) A.

Axiom Alge: forall x: R, ((-1) * (-1 * x) = x)%R.
